---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
import Logo from "../images/logo-alt.svg?raw";
---

<footer
  class="bg-primary-darker py-8 px-16 md:py-24 md:px-60 mx-auto text-center md:text-left"
>
<p 
    class=" text-white mb-6 p-4 text-left bg-primary-default rounded"
  >
  PLEASE BE ADVISED THAT IF YOU RUN CODE INCLUDED IN THESE PLUGINS OR USE INFORMATION GENERATED BY THESE PLUGINS, INCLUDING MAKING ANY DECISIONS BASED UPON THE INFORMATION, YOU DO SO AT YOUR OWN RISK. GREEN SOFTWARE FOUNDATION MAKES NO REPRESENTATION, GUARANTEE OR WARRANTY, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, STATUTORY OR OTHERWISE, INCLUDING MERCHANTABILITY OR FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE NOR ANY WARRANTIES ARISING FROM COURSE OF PERFORMANCE, COURSE OF DEALING OR USAGE IN TRADE.
  </p>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 md:space-x-24">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <span class="w-40 mx-auto md:mx-0">
        <Fragment set:html={Logo} />
      </span>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs font-normal pt-4">
        Copyright Â© {year} Joint Development Foundation Projects, LLC, Green Software
        Foundation Series <br /><br /> The Joint Development Foundation Projects,
        LLC is an affiliate of the Linux Foundation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Links -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 pt-8">
      <h1 class="uppercase text-accent-default font-bold text-xs relative">
        Links
        <span
          class="hidden md:flex absolute left-0 -bottom-1 h-[2px] w-4 bg-accent-default space-y-6"
        ></span>
      </h1>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://grnsft.org/if/how-to-submit-plugin"
          class="text-xs text-gray-300">How to submit a plugin</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://grnsft.org/champions/chairguide"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs text-gray-300">For GSF Project & WG Chairs</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Green-Software-Foundation/champions"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs text-gray-300">GitHub Repo</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Legal  -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 pt-8">
      <h1 class="uppercase text-accent-default font-bold text-xs relative">
        Legal
        <span
          class="hidden md:flex absolute left-0 -bottom-1 h-[2px] w-4 bg-accent-default space-y-6"
        ></span>
      </h1>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://greensoftware.foundation/policy/trademark"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs text-gray-300">Trademark Policy</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://greensoftware.foundation/policy/terms"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs text-gray-300">Privacy Policy</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://greensoftware.foundation/policy/terms"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs text-gray-300">Terms and Conditions</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- GSF Info -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 pt-8">
      <h1 class="uppercase text-accent-default font-bold text-xs relative">
        GSF Info
        <span
          class="hidden md:flex absolute left-0 -bottom-1 h-[2px] w-4 bg-accent-default space-y-6"
        ></span>
      </h1>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://greensoftware.foundation/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs text-gray-300">Website</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://twitter.com/gsfcommunity"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs text-gray-300">Twitter</a
        >
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/green-software-foundation/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs text-gray-300">LinkedIn</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</footer>
